<div class="allocation-finalize">
	<h2>Allocating {{team.team_name}} to {{project.project_name}}</h2>
	{{#if isAuthorized}}
		<p>You will be sending these emails through {{outlookUser.EmailAddress}} as {{outlookUser.DisplayName}}.</p>
		<p>After this process, the project will be allocated to the team {{team.team_name}}, and will be set as a preliminary assignment.</p><br>
		<h2>Email to the students</h2>
		<div id="teamSubjectEdit" class="email-editor-title"><b>Subject</b> <i class="fa fa-edit"></i></div>
		<div id="teamBodyEdit" class="email-editor" contenteditable="true">{{{teamEmail.emailSubject}}}</div><br>
		<div class="email-editor-title"><b>Body</b> <i class="fa fa-edit"></i></div>
		<div class="email-editor" contenteditable="true">{{{teamEmail.emailBody}}}</div><br>
	{{else}}
		<p>You need to be signed into a Microsoft account to proceed to the next step.</p>
		<p id='continue-message' style="display: none">Once you have successfully signed in on the pop-up window, please click Continue.</p>
		<button id='login-msft' class='project-block-btn' onclick='microsoftAuthenticateAlloc("{{outlook_authenticate}}")'>Login here</button>
		<button id='login-next' class='project-block-btn' onclick='allocateTeam({{team.team_id}}, {{project.project_id}}, false)'>Continue</button>
	{{/if}}
	<p>You can also override this step by sending a manual email through your preferred email client.</p>
	<button id='overrideBtn' class='project-block-btn' onclick='sendManualEmail("{{#team.students_in_teams}}{{students.qut_email}},{{/team.students_in_teams}}")'>Send Manual Email</button>
	<button id='sentBtn' class='project-block-btn' onclick='allocateTeam({{team.team_id}}, {{project.project_id}}, true)'>Sent?</button>
</div>